            <p class="text-sm text-gray-800 mb-4">A Hawaii dermatology practice needed more than referrals to grow. They wanted predictable, scalable patient acquisition that could keep pace with their expansion.</p>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-400 mb-1">The Solution</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-800 mb-4">Built a paid search system designed to scale delivering consistent new patient flow month after month while maintaining cost efficiency.</p>
